features: Hardcover Leather Notebook: The front and back cover are made of unique vegan leather with solid cardboard to ensure durable and organized feature. Elastic band closure with 4 golden corner-protectors keeps your writing journal safe in the backpack to carry around.

Twin-wire Journal Notebook: Strong metal wire rings, double wire bound construction helps turn the pages easily, lay flat to write comfortably for both right and left handed customers, as well as flip the cover back. Golden spiral bound adds aesthetic matching.

Fountain Pen Paper Notebook: 100 GSM ivory paper provides no bleeding through, no smearing, no ghosting or no feathering writing experience for you. We combines sophisticated style and high quality paper to create a reliable notebook journal for your writing.

300 Pages Spiral Journal: 8.5"x11", standard letter size with 150 sheets/300 pages college ruled paper to last all year, and acid-free paper avoids yellow over time. “Memo No” and “Date” are at the top of each page for classification and reference.

Subject Notebook Sticky Tabs: 6 Different colors to classify multi subjects quickly; 24 PCS thick tabs for easy to write on both sides, for sticky to flip through, for easy to remove and reposition. Perfect to mark, index, reference, highlighter and divide neat and easy.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Exclusively vegan leather with solid cardboard makes a sturdy hard cover to protect notebook and nice texture to touch.Durable golden spiral bound, large dual metal rings helps turn pages easily, lay completely flat to write comfortably and 360° flip the cover to back.Elastic band keeps the notebook closed without falling out and works as bookmarks.Each cover corner has golden corner protector to prevent getting worn down or accidentally folding, and add aesthetic.The front cover and back cover is inserted with a large inner pocket for loose leaf paper, receipts, stickers, tabs to organize.Classic Black, Teal and Cute Pink, 3 unique colors for options, eye-attractive spiral notebook gifts for women, men, girls and boys, take the favourite color for yourself, your families, friends and the one you are missing now.Amanple, a professional notebook journal manufacturer, has been committed to market researching, professional designing and producing various notebooks worldwide. Now we sell our owned brand products directly to our customers to meet your demands on paper, cover, binding and smooth writing experience.

300 Pages/150 sheets are designed for performance and offer plenty of writing space to last all year.8.5" x 11", letter size has plenty of space for taking notes all-in-one, and suitable for backpack or briefcase.Ivory-white color paper, a great job of showing off ink colors,is easier on the eyes and can give your writing a more refined feel.Pages are acid-free and won't yellow over time to keep your writing forever.100 GSM thick paper is highly resistant to feathering, bleedthrough and ghosting to draw or write on both sides of the paper.College Ruled Paper, 7mm lines spacing with a space on the top line for “Title” and “Date/No” to keep your ideas tidy.24 Pcs sticky index tabs, 6 different color for assortment to work as subject notebook.

Premium vegan leather provides soft and smooth texture to touch.Hard cover is better to get knocked around for daily use and provide a rigid writing surface if you’re jotting down an entry away from a desk. Metal wire ring makes it easy to tear out pages without disturbing the rest of the notebook. Large double wirebound helps you turn the page easily and you can rest comfortably on the notebook or desk as you write. If you carry your journals around, the elastic band will keep your notebook closed to protect notebook’s pages—and add a feeling of privacy.It can also work as bookmark to mark your last spot.
Inner Pockets 2 Large paper pockets on the coverHigh capacity to store business cards, loose leaf paper, receipts, bills, stickers, rulers, and small slim items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I journal every day. I know exactly what I want: creamy paper, narrow ruling, spiral bound, THICK BOOK! This is a dream come true. The metal corners are a benefit that never occurred to me before, but I want them always! This journal is so elegant that my penmanship is much better. I guess my fingers are trying to be worthy of the book! 😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A serious notebook
reviews.reviewText: This thing is huge! Full page sized and plenty of it too. It’s very sturdy with a spiral bind and even had these metal corners to protect the cover. It has an elastic closure, pretty gold spiral and a pocket inside. No complaints. It should last me a while.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great color, high quality materials, thick paper. Will buy again. The dark green is luxurious.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High Quality Notebook
reviews.reviewText: I had very high expectations for the price, and this passed. The cover is very sturdy and a nice green color. The corner protectors are an appreciated touch. So many pages! which makes it thick but worth the money. Comes with sticky dividers and a strap to keep it shut/bookmark.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High Quality Product!
reviews.reviewText: I was definitely surprised when I received this notebook. I honestly thought it would be a flimsy cardboard cover with ok pages. I was definitely wrong in every regard. I am very pleased with the sturdiness of the cover and spiral spine material. The page weight is perfect and very smooth when writing on it. Thank you for a wonderful product! I’m definitely hard on my notebooks and other similar items, I am pleased to say I won’t be looking any further for my notebooks. These are the ones to buy and are reasonably priced.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful notebook, a little heavy
reviews.reviewText: Great book for journaling, notes and general scribbles. Bookmark strap is great for keeping your place. A lot of clean, thick pages with nice spacing. Tabs are a nice touch. It is a large notebook with hard covers and is therefore a little on the heavy side, so keep that in mind for ease of transport and comfort.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The cover is absolutely lovely, excellent quality hardcover notebook. The paper is thick enough that the only bleed through was with a Sharpie (which is expected to bleed through pretty much any paper). See my photos for example, the yellow is highlighter, which also did not bleed through. The spiral is nice and thick, looks and feels like it will keep its shape and not be easily crushed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Eye catching, you can number pages & has a table of contents for you to record. Place for date at top of page & circle day of week. Lined & comes with a few stick on divider tabs. I LOVE this book. Endless uses. I use it for daily lists. Cover is thick with gold corners!!!
Me encanto por que las hojas son gruesas y de muy buena calidad la libreta y el espiral
